flowchart
Class FlowchartSymbolFactory

java.lang.Object
  flowchart.FlowchartSymbolFactory
public class FlowchartSymbolFactory
extends java.lang.Object

This is a factory for creating symbols in a flowchart. The symbols includes processing boxes, empty boxes, condition diamonds, start points, end points, and directed edges. The connection points (i.e. ports in JGraph) for each cell are also created.

Version:
1.00 (Last update: June 8, 2008)
Author:
Dr. Wen-jun LI, Da LUO
